  h2='Hedgehog'
  p I did not know people owned hedgehogs as pets until I saw a classmate from highschool post about her new hedgehog. When I asked my dad if I could get one he flat out said no. Apparently he had one when he was younger and it was a vicious little thing. I think he didn't hold it enough when he first got it (I read all about owning and caring for a hedgehog and if you don't let it associate you with your scent it can be mean. They're pretty blind so they notice people by scent). Plus I've learned they love to cuddle with you.p
